People thanks for making this happen 10 MILLION VIEWS for the lyric video and more than 9 MILLION VIEWS on the official video, thanks for making this happen happen again and shout out to my precious girl🙈 Lauren, no matter what I love that lovely raspy voice she has it's so unique, and tbh she's got me paralyzed with that song, let's keep supporting her in every thing she does in the future...getting back to her I love how she defends her self and how she also just doesn't think about her self she also thinks about her people and use the harmonizers and the laurenators how she tries to defend us by using her voice how no matter what situation she's going through in her life she's always there for us to stand for us and to put on a great show, to make us feel better and just make us feel the life with her music, and who ever is reading this I'm so thankful for y'all making her career shine and we're all in this together to make her dreams keep going, give a fuck to the others who say that she has no talent because she really does, give a fuck to people who say she's just a princess popstar⭐🌟 because she's more than that,and just don't listen to this bitches because they have no fuckin idea of wtf they're talking about, because she's everything to the true harmonizers like us, she's more than just a popstar...shes a brave and a courageous woman who keeps making us not quit in life who says what she has in her mind, and who's not afraid of anything, she's really special to me in every kinda way, like for the lgbt group, even if I'm not gay, lesbian bisexual, or transgender, even if I'm nothing of those tittles it doesn't matter because people who are in the lgbt group they're still lovely human beings and they don't deserve to be discriminated, they are people who belong. And secondly she's always interested in the feminism there is, in my words every women on this world no matter what age or sexuality our lovely women have, y'all are all special, brave, unique, beautiful, gorgeous women ♀, don't let nothing step in your way or stop you, no one or man is in charge from y'alls actions. And so very special to me, she's the one who at least try to do something for our world these days like the NRA, and immigrants that I really care about and I'm really curious from what they are going through🖑...so let's keep supporting her in every thing, let's do the same for, let's keep being there for when she needs our company and opinions💐. Thanks for anyone who's reading this🙄
